1
00:00:42,479 --> 00:00:45,159
If the Key of Fate's user

2
00:00:46,119 --> 00:00:47,520
passes the ten-year mark, what happens?

3
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,840
They'll truly become that person.

4
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,159
In this world,

5
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:53,439
there's no way to switch back ever again.

6
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:56,960
I see.

7
00:00:58,479 --> 00:00:59,320
Why ask that?

8
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:00,799
Nothing.

9
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,359
I just wanted to know how it ends.

10
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,200
No matter how it ends,

11
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:09,719
once you choose,

12
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,680
you can only See it through to the end.

13
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:13,319
Otherwise,

14
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,760
it Hurts us both.

15
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,040
Sorry, Si Qi.

16
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,120
I'm late.

17
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,400
You're not late.

18
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,159
Let's go.

19
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,519
Where to?

20
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,239
Well... didn't you say last time

21
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,680
you'd treat me to dinner as a thank you?

22
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,480
You get to pick what we eat.

23
00:01:59,280 --> 00:01:59,959
We...

24
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,840
Is... is this a date?

25
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,280
We...

26
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,719
I'm kidding.

27
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:16,439
It's just that this mall

28
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,520
doesn't really have anything good to eat.

29
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,879
Have you ever played the claw machine?

30
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,680
I haven't.

31
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,800
I want to try it out.

32
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:27,680
Come on.

33
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,360
Let's go.

34
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:35,319
Think I can get it?

35
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,039
Nope.

36
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:50,159
Again.

37
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,240
Again.

38
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,960
What was that? Ugh, so close.

39
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,599
Let me.

40
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,759
Watch this.

41
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,560
You're amazing!

42
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:15,960
How was that?

43
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:29,360
As long as you like it.

44
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:34,039
Here's your favorite Danzai ice cream.

45
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,319
Strawberry flavor.

46
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,199
I've got another surprise for you.

47
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,199
Your birthday's in a few days.

48
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:48,400
But I want to celebrate it with you now.

49
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,039
You didn't get to eat

50
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:52,199
that hotel cake you wanted last time.

51
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,319
So I'm making it up to you this time.

52
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,159
I'm sorry.

53
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,800
You didn't have to do this.

54
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,719
Because on my birthday, I'll definitely still in—

55
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,400
Make a wish.

56
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:27,160
I'm really happy today.

57
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,959
I've got someone to share cake with.

58
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:29,600
Thank you.

59
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:30,879
You're welcome.

60
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,680
Watch where you're riding!

61
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,439
Are you okay?

62
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,839
Sorry, Si Qi.

63
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,839
This isn't right for us.

64
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,439
Yeah.

65
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:29,879
Th-this...

66
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,560
I...

67
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,199
I don't know what's wrong with me lately.

68
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,199
I don't know why,

69
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,639
but I'm even doubting myself now.

70
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,160
Between you and Xiaobei,

71
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,480
I find myself wanting to be closer to you.

72
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,000
You feel more familiar.

73
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,519
I don't know why.

74
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,079
You understand me better,

75
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,560
you know what I'm thinking.

76
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,439
I'm really starting to doubt myself.

77
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,240
Sorry, Si Qi.

78
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,720
I...

79
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:11,399
You didn't do anything wrong.

80
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:14,120
I'm the one with the problem.

81
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,560
You don't need to apologize.

82
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,120
It's late.

83
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,079
Go back and get some rest.

84
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,279
Um...

85
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,759
Zhang Xiaobei...

86
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,040
is he treating you well?

87
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,399
Xiaobei and I

88
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,480
already broke up.

89
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,199
Even before my dad was hospitalized,

90
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,120
my feelings for him seemed to have changed.

91
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:26,120
From when my dad was hospitalized

92
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:30,120
to when he passed away,

93
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,360
you were by my side the whole time.

94
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:41,639
So, actually...

95
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:46,240
Actually, I...

96
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,319
Wait until I'm done with all this.

97
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,000
If I can still come back,

98
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,759
and you don't hate me that much,

99
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,800
you can tell me the rest then.

100
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,720
She's still waiting for me.

101
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:00,879
Sheng Yuanzhou.

102
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,120
After all, she's my fiancee now.

103
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,560
If I hadn't shown up just now,

104
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:33,919
were you going to tell her the truth?

105
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,039
I won't.

106
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,679
Like you said,

107
00:08:38,399 --> 00:08:40,639
since we chose this, we must See it through to the end.

108
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,440
Otherwise, it Hurts us both.

109
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:47,000
I will absolutely never let Si Qi

110
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,639
suffer even the slightest bit of harm.

111
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,840
Then what if one day

112
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:54,000
she finds out her love was an illusion?

113
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,480
How do you think she'll live with that?

114
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,639
Sometimes,

115
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:01,480
the most painful thing isn't the lie,

116
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,519
it's the truth.

117
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,440
Get out!

118
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,039
You're not my husband!

119
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:10,000
You're a monster!

120
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,759
Give me back Sheng Shizhong!

121
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,039
Give him back!

122
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,919
I'll never let Si Qi suffer the same fate.

123
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,840
Si Qi!

124
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,120
Why did you lie to me?

125
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:38,799
I didn't mean to.

126
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,720
Let me explain.

127
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,320
I don't want to hear it.

128
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,759
It's too late.

129
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,039
Thank goodness it was just a dream.

130
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,480
I absolutely cannot let Si Qi

131
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,080
suffer the same fate as Bai Zimei.

132
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,480
Hello, Mr. Sheng.

133
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,960
You've worked hard this time.

134
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,279
It's for the company's development.

135
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,080
It's my duty.

136
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,600
After I finish this business meeting,

137
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:12,679
I have a meeting with Mr. Wang from Yongsheng Group.

138
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,320
If we close the deal,

139
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,919
the company's year-end results

140
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,480
can go up another two percentage points.

141
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,120
Good work.

142
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,919
But don't overdo it.

143
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,240
Your hand's still injured.

144
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,519
I've hired a driver for you,

145
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,120
so while you're on the road,

146
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,360
you can get some more rest.

147
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,120
Those who achieve great things

148
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,720
must not waste their energy.

149
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:33,919
Thank you, Father.

150
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,279
Mr. Zhang.

151
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,519
Chairman Sheng, Mr. Sheng.

152
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:41,960
Later, Mr. Sheng

153
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,080
is going to Yongsheng Group.

154
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,360
Drive and take good care of him.

155
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,879
No problem, no problem.

156
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,679
Thank you for the opportunity, boss.

157
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:53,879
Father.

158
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,120
I... I'm used to driving myself.

159
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:59,120
Successful people must leave trivial matters

160
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,039
to ordinary people.

161
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,879
Thank you, Father.

162
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:10,879
I heard

163
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,639
your family runs a breakfast shop, right?

164
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,600
Why are you out here driving for someone?

165
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:19,360
The landlord suddenly took the place back.

166
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:21,279
So we can't run the breakfast shop anymore.

167
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,360
Took it back?

168
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:23,399
Why?

169
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,480
I don't know the exact reason.

170
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,080
Since we were renting it on credit,

171
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,799
when they said they were taking it back,

172
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:31,320
we couldn't really say anything.

173
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,039
So I had to come out and find a job.

174
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:35,320
Then Mr. Sheng came to me in person.

175
00:11:35,639 --> 00:11:37,039
Said he wanted to assign you a driver.

176
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,639
And the pay's pretty good.

177
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,440
So I came.

178
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:44,000
He personally went to find a driver?

179
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:47,120
Did Sheng Shizhong see through my identity,

180
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,759
and use my dad to test me on purpose?

181
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,399
I'm the one who took it back.

182
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:56,759
You're violating

183
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:57,759
the agreement between us.

184
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:59,399
I'm just giving you a warning.

185
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,840
You have nothing right now.

186
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,080
If you walk away,

187
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:04,320
you won't even be able to support your parents.

188
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,159
You care that much about how I treat Si Qi.

189
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:12,120
Don't tell me you...

190
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:15,399
Don't flatter yourself.

191
00:12:15,879 --> 00:12:17,399
I just don't want a losing deal.

192
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,360
I don't want any uncertainty

193
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,679
messing up my plan.

194
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,159
Remember this.

195
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:26,000
Before you gain real power in the Sheng family,

196
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,679
you have no right to choose.

197
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:38,799
What brings you here?

198
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:40,919
You're well-connected.

199
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,320
I need a chance to make money.

200
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,679
Move fast.

201
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,399
Ever heard of the Keke Fund?

202
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,440
They do home rentals and sales.

203
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,840
A rental-sales model brought in from Korea.

204
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,679
It's been a huge hit here.

205
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,799
It should see a huge spike soon.

206
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,960
Then that plot of land I had before,

207
00:12:58,879 --> 00:12:59,879
can I mortgage it again?

208
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:01,840
No way.

209
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,279
Last time you said you didn't want to alert your dad.

210
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:06,440
So I had to find a private lender.

211
00:13:07,039 --> 00:13:08,440
People who can pull out that much cash at once

212
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,240
are hard to come by.

213
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,320
I went through a lot of trouble

214
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,360
just to find one for you.

215
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,159
But then you,

216
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,559
you just decided not to mortgage it.

217
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:14,879
Now you want me to find someone again?

218
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:15,840
Where am I supposed to look?

219
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,799
Unless...

220
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,039
Unless what?

221
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,480
You sell it.

222
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,960
That's the inheritance Sheng Yuanzhou's mom left him.

223
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,080
And I'm supposed to sell it?

224
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,720
If you really can't bear to part with it,

225
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,320
just sell it and buy it back later.

226
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:37,600
Don't you want some capital to make money anyway?

227
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:38,480
Fine.

228
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:39,840
Act fast.

229
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,200
The faster, the better.

230
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:45,320
You can count on me.

231
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:48,159
Mr. Sheng, Mr. Sheng!

232
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:48,840
Have some water.

233
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:52,799
Sorry, sorry.

234
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:53,279
It's fine, it's fine.

235
00:13:53,639 --> 00:13:55,600
Mr. Sheng, I got your clothes dirty, didn't I?

236
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:59,200
I can drive the car myself.

237
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:00,720
You don't need to stay with me anymore.

238
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,039
I... I...

239
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:04,159
Mr. Sheng, that was my fault just now.

240
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:06,559
Please don't fire me.

241
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:09,799
My family really needs the money.

242
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,919
There's 20,000 yuan in this card.

243
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,879
Consider it your pay for this month.

244
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:19,120
From now on, every month,

245
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,679
I'll transfer some money into it.

246
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,360
I don't mean to fire you.

247
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,559
I'm...

248
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:27,159
just not used to being waited on.

249
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:29,320
Please don't tell Father about this.

250
00:14:30,519 --> 00:14:32,080
I won't tell Chairman Sheng.

251
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,039
Mr. Sheng...

252
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,000
You...

253
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,039
You're really a good person.

254
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,919
Good people will be rewarded.

255
00:14:41,639 --> 00:14:42,799
Alright, since you're free now,

256
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:43,720
just take a walk around,

257
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,000
and head back early to rest.

258
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,000
Alright.

259
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,039
Then I'll head back first.

260
00:14:47,879 --> 00:14:48,720
You're really a good person.

261
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,440
Go on, go on.

262
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:54,159
Sheng Shizhong.

263
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:58,480
I will definitely settle this score for my dad.
